    "        k = random.randint(0, n - 1)\n",
    "        if k not in selected_nodes:\n",
    "            break\n",
    "    selected_nodes.append(k)\n",
    "\n",
    "selected_nodes.sort()\n",
    "print(\"selected_nodes: \", selected_nodes)\n",

    "    print(\"current node: \", node)\n",

    "        if e in edgeList:\n",
    "            print(\"removing: \", e)\n",
    "            edgeList.remove(e)\n",
    "            G.remove_edge(*e)"

    "def create_input_graph(n_nodes, Smax):\n",
    "    G = nx.complete_graph(n_nodes)\n",
    "    edgeList = list(G.edges)\n",
    "    nodeList = list(G.nodes)\n",
    "    m = G.number_of_edges() - 1\n",
    "    selected_nodes = []\n",
    "    n = n_nodes\n",
    "    n_small = int(2 * np.log(n))\n",
    "    for i in range(n_small):\n",
    "        while(True):\n",
    "            k = random.randint(0, n - 1)\n",
    "            if k not in selected_nodes:\n",
    "                break\n",
    "        selected_nodes.append(k)\n",
    "\n",
    "    selected_nodes.sort()\n",
    "    others = list(set(nodeList) - set(selected_nodes))\n",
    "    print(\"selected_nodes: \", selected_nodes)\n",
    "    print(\"others: \", others)\n",
    "\n",
    "    k = len(others) + 1 #if we assign the selected nodes in one room, and everyone else in their own room\n",
    "    print(\"k: \", k)\n",
    "    Sroom = Smax / k\n",
    "    S_selected = Sroom\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(\"assigning values for selected nodes\")\n",
    "    for i in range(n_small):\n",
    "        node = selected_nodes.pop(0);\n",
    "        print(\"current node: \", node)\n",
    "        for other_node in selected_nodes:\n",
    "            e = (node, other_node)\n",
    "            edgeList.remove(e)\n",
    "            happiness = round(random.uniform(0, 100), 3)\n",
    "            stress = round(random.uniform(0, S_selected), 3)\n",
    "            G.add_edge(node, other_node, happiness=happiness, stress=stress)\n",
    "            print(\"edge: {}, h:{}, s:{}\".format(e,happiness,stress))\n",
    "            S_selected -= stress\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(\"assigning values for other nodes\")\n",
    "    for i in range(len(edgeList)):\n",
    "        e = edgeList.pop(0);\n",
    "        happiness = round(random.uniform(0, 100), 3)\n",
    "        stress = round(random.uniform(0, Sroom), 3)\n",
    "        G.add_edge(e[0], e[1], happiness=happiness, stress=stress)\n",
    "        print(\"edge: {}, h:{}, s:{}\".format(e,happiness,stress))\n",
    "    return G"
   ]
